title: Squarish sans numbers on Fort Dunlop building in Birmingham
content:
Hey, I wonder if anyone can tell me what this font is thats used for the numbers on the Fort Dunlop building in Birmingham. Thanks in advance..!

[http://furryvision.com/fort\_dunlop.jpg](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018101802/http:/furryvision.com/fort_dunlop.jpg)
author: furryvision

comments.content: Not an exact match, but [Wedding Sans](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018101802/http:/www.typecuts.com/fonts_view.php?kid=2&sid=28) would be quite close.
